'''Void Mayonnaise''' is an [[Artisan Goods|Artisan Good]] made by placing a [[Void Egg]] inside the [[Mayonnaise Machine]]. It may be also be fished from the [[Witch's Swamp]] (25% chance if the player does not have one in inventory).  Players may only fish a Void Mayonnaise from the [[Witch's Swamp]] while the [[Henchman]] is guarding the [[Witch's Hut]].  Gifting a Void Mayonnaise to the Henchman outside the [[Witch's Hut]] will allow players to pass during the quest [[Quests#Goblin Problem|Goblin Problem]].

